# 🌆 Smart City Analysis Dashboard

## 📌 Project Overview

This project is an interactive Power BI dashboard developed to analyze the performance and development of smart cities in India. It provides insights into ICT scores, internet connectivity, public transport, smart electricity, water supply, and e-Government services through interactive visualizations and filters.

---

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies

- Power BI
- Microsoft Excel
- Data Visualization

---

## 📊 Dashboard Features

- Internet Accessibility Analysis
- 4G Coverage Analysis
- Smart Electricity Analysis
- Public Transport Analysis
- Water Supply Insights
- e-Government Services
- ICT Score Analysis
- City-wise Analysis
- Year-wise Analysis
- Interactive Filters and Slicers

---

## 📄 Dashboard

The dashboard provides:

- Internet Accessibility
- 4G Coverage
- Smart Electricity
- Public Transport
- Water Supply
- e-Government Services
- ICT Score Analysis
- Public Wi-Fi Availability
- Top Smart Cities
- Year-wise Development

